FBIS4-55222 "dreeu092_b_94004" FBIS-EEU-94-092 Daily Report 11 May 1994 BULGARIA New Alliance Deputy Offered Justice Post New Alliance Deputy Offered Justice Post AU1105141694 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1300 GMT 11 May 94 AU1105141694 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Bulgarian BFN [Text] Gospodin Atanasov, deputy for the New Alliance for Democracy, confirmed today that Prime Minister Lyuben Berov offered him the post minister of justice in the new cabinet he is forming. Gospodin Atanasov said that he is ready to accept the proposal, even against the wishes of his own parliamentary faction, but the issue has not yet been definitely decided.
